message.raw:
Audited g07a connection table after massive ANZAC day rewiring. Settings in BLACS to yield equivalent values before rewiring. Need to check:
* MOT_repump_lock and optical_pumping amplitudes (DDS driving AOMs has changed),
* digital gates on novatechdds9m_9
Unit conversions included for Bq, but frequency unit conversions omitted until base unit is standardised between BLACS and labscript. Compiled connection table against w-cl27-g07a-control_globals.h5 in runmanager for the first time - required renaming output h5 file to w-cl27-g07a-control.h5. Seems to work fine, but haven't tried running an experiment.
